tests.name: Game Lobby Page should match snapshot when rendered.
Game Lobby Page should set head title and meta tags when rendered.
Game Lobby Page Small Screen Toast should add info toast for small screen after 200ms when screen is smaller than md.
Game Lobby Page Small Screen Toast should not add info toast for small screen after 200ms when screen is not smaller than md.
Game Lobby Page Small Screen Toast should not add info toast for small screen when screen is smaller than md but 200ms have not passed.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Players Party should reset create game dto when rendered.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Players Party should reset game when rendered.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Players Party should load all audios when rendered.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Role Picker should open role picker modal when game lobby players party emits pick role for player event.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Role Picker should not open role picker modal when game lobby players party emits pick role for player event with no player.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Role Picker should throw error when game lobby players party emits pick role for player event but the role picker is not found in refs.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Options Hub should open game lobby options hub when game lobby players party emits open options hub event.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Options Hub should throw error when game lobby header emits game options button click event but the options hub is not found in refs.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Position Coordinator should open game lobby position coordinator when game lobby players party emits position coordinator button click event.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Position Coordinator should throw error when game lobby header emits position coordinator button click event but the position coordinator is not found in refs.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Additional Cards Manager should open game lobby additional cards manager when game lobby players party emits additional cards button click event.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Additional Cards Manager should throw error when game lobby header emits additional cards button click event but the additional cards manager is not found in refs.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Group Organizer should open game lobby group organizer when game lobby players party emits group organizer button click event.
Game Lobby Page Game Lobby Group Organizer should throw error when game lobby header emits group organizer button click event but the group organizer is not found in refs.
Game Lobby Page Reject Players Position Step should throw error when reject players position step event is emitted by footer but header is not defined in refs.
Game Lobby Page Reject Players Position Step should highlight position coordinator button when reject players position step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Players Position Step should open position coordinator after timeout when reject players position step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Thief or Actor Additional Cards Placed Step should throw error when reject thief additional cards placed step event is emitted by footer but header is not defined in refs.
Game Lobby Page Reject Thief or Actor Additional Cards Placed Step should highlight additional cards manager button when reject thief additional cards placed step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Thief or Actor Additional Cards Placed Step should open additional cards manager after timeout when reject thief additional cards placed step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Thief or Actor Additional Cards Placed Step should throw error when reject actor additional cards placed step event is emitted by footer but header is not defined in refs.
Game Lobby Page Reject Thief or Actor Additional Cards Placed Step should highlight additional cards manager button when reject actor additional cards placed step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Game Options Changed Step should throw error when reject game options changed step event is emitted by footer but header is not defined in refs.
Game Lobby Page Reject Game Options Changed Step should highlight game options button when reject game options changed step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Reject Game Options Changed Step should open game options hub after timeout when reject game options changed step event is emitted by footer.
Game Lobby Page Inject player from query should set players to create game dto when query is fulfilled with player names.
Game Lobby Page Inject player from query should not set players to create game dto when query is not fulfilled with player names.
Game Page should match snapshot when rendered.
Game Page should set head title and meta tags when rendered.
Game Page should fetch and set game in store when rendered with valid game id as string.
Game Page should fetch and set game in store when rendered with valid game id as array of strings.
Game Page should load all audios when rendered.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render game is loading container when game fetching status is pending.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render loading game spinner with text when game fetching status is pending.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render game not found when game fetching status is error.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render playing game when game fetching status is success and game status is playing.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render game over when game fetching status is success and game status is over.
Game Page Game Status Containers should render game canceled when game fetching status is success and game status is canceled.
Game Page Game is found should show game feedback submitter when game component emits a game feedback submitter button click.
Game Page Game is found should throw an error when game component emits a game feedback submitter button click and game feedback submitter is not defined.
Game Page Unmount should fade out playing background audio when unmounted.
Index Page Component should match snapshot when rendered.
Index Page Component Title should display translated title when rendered.
Index Page Component Subtitle should translate subtitle when rendered.
Index Page Component Play button should display play button with translated label when rendered.
Index Page Component Play button Play Button Icon should not have animation class when not hovered.
Index Page Component Play button Play Button Icon should have animation class when hovered.
Index Page Component About button should display about button with translated label when rendered.
Index Page Component About button About Button Icon should not have animation class when not hovered.
Index Page Component About button About Button Icon should have animation class when hovered.
Error Component should match snapshot when rendered.
Error Component Error Title should set head title of error title when rendered.
Error Component Error Title should render page not found title when error status code is 404.
Error Component Error Title should render unexpected error title when error status code is not 404.
Error Component Lottie Error should set size to lottie when rendered.
Error Component Error description should render page not found description when error status code is 404.
Error Component Error description should render unexpected error description when error status code is not 404.
App Component should match snapshot when rendered.
App Component should render component without shallow and match snapshot when rendered.
App Component should define OgImage when rendered.
App Component should set head title and meta tags when rendered.
App Component should fetch and set roles from store when rendered.
App Component should set howler audio settings from audio store when rendered.
About Page Component should match snapshot when rendered.
About Page Component should set head title and meta tags when rendered.
About Page Component Title should display role image of werewolf when rendered.
About Page Component Title should display translated title when rendered.
